articles.description:
Elon Musk announced last night that Tesla is planning to â€œroughly doubleâ€ its Robotaxi fleet in Austin next month. While an expansion of the pilot sounds positive on the surface, a look at the actual numbers reveals that Tesla is missing its own â€œend of yearâ€ target by a massive margin.
